ai_prompts.cursor_vercel_deployment:
Set up production deployment with Vercel:

```bash
# Install Vercel CLI
npm install -g vercel

# Configure deployment
vercel login
vercel --prod

# Create vercel.json configuration
cat > vercel.json << 'EOF'
{
  "framework": "nextjs",
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "outputDirectory": ".next",
  "installCommand": "npm install",
  "env": {
    "NODE_ENV": "production"
  },
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "X-Content-Type-Options",
          "value": "nosniff"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-Frame-Options",
          "value": "DENY"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
EOF
```

